{"tid":1989420,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"一組神秘「信德語」導致全球 iPhone 出現閃退當機","createTime":"2020-04-26T03:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T22:03:43.000Z","uid":49136,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"72bebedff2211c9dad3ac3a8e991757857b454a3","tid":1989420,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:17:48.000Z","msg":"還記得過去只要收到特殊文字就能造成 iPhone 順間崩潰閃退 Bug 嗎？在最新 iOS 13.4.1 系統中，又再度被 EverythingApplePro 發現意大利國旗 Emoji 和信德語（南亞巴基斯坦信德人語言）組成的文字即可讓通訊軟體造成閃退或設備當機，除了 iPhone 會受影響外，連同 iPad 和 Apple Watch 也無一倖免。<br />\n<br />\n這次文字 Bug 如先前錯誤相同，但結果都是雷同，除了在瀏覽器\b、通訊（如LINE、 WhatsApp、Twitter 等）或社群軟體 App 內顯示這組特殊信德語文字符號就有機會導致崩潰外，如果直接複製這組信德語，會直接造成卡頓當機，整台設備完全會無法觸控。<br />\n<br />\n這波信德語惡作劇攻擊，也造成多數國外用戶在打開 Twitter 等多款 App 時，都會出現錯誤並且立即導致閃退現象。<br />\n<br />\n比較誇張的是國外用戶惡意在 Twitter、Facebook 社群軟體大量傳輸這串特殊信德語，導致不少 iPhone 設備直接看見有夾帶這串符號，甚至是手動複製就會造成 iOS 系統崩潰重開機，如果是在 App 內顯示，也會循環造成閃退或進入安全模式。<br />\n<br />\n目前暫時解決方法只有將設備強制重開機，並且將 App 推出後台或是重新安裝或是升級到 iOS 13.4.5 Beta新版本，才能夠暫時解決。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果尚未針對這項錯誤作出回應，不過這次義大利國旗配合信德語造成錯誤過去也曾發生過，\b主要是因為 iOS 系統在合併兩組 Emoji 時，會需要處理大量內容，容易出現指令無法完成，最後造成系統崩潰或當機。<br />\n<br />\niOS 13.4.1 也存在郵件App零時差漏洞（Zero-Day），目前在 iOS 13.4.5 2Beta 已經修補信德語錯誤，相信蘋果會在近期推出 iOS 13 正式版更新。<br />\n<br />\n如果是越獄用戶，可透過另一款「插件」搶先修正錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/ios-crash-text-bug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fios-crash-text-bug&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=716990ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/ios-crash-text-bug</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小心使用</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d8fba336b7180962f7cbd60339727f0e1a9efb","tid":1989420,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"btw 連登無效 tg有效"},{"pid":"973e27b7dd468032c34b9e274171e6eff7522ac8","tid":1989420,"uid":105678,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"點解IOS可以成日出現呢啲弱智問題=,="},{"pid":"3e9421e9b18f53c65e3dc0edcc9e866e9a563bcc","tid":1989420,"uid":228140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:28:47.000Z","msg":":بٍٍٍٍََُُُِّّّْرٍٍٍٍََُُِِّّّْآٍٍٍَُّ🇮🇹 بٍٍٍٍََُُُِّّّْرٍٍٍٍََُُِِّّّْآٍٍٍَُّ🇮🇹"},{"pid":"9ea765c6426df761209e2c63c0c1db8282e98e50","tid":1989420,"uid":49136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3e9421e9b18f53c65e3dc0edcc9e866e9a563bcc","tid":1989420,"uid":228140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:28:47.000Z","msg":":بٍٍٍٍََُُُِّّّْرٍٍٍٍََُُِِّّّْآٍٍٍَُّ🇮🇹 بٍٍٍٍََُُُِّّّْرٍٍٍٍََُُِِّّّْآٍٍٍَُّ🇮🇹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"我試過youtube有效<br />\n大家唔好去藍youtuber試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a518f376760da2f05691b094d8cb3a2af6b9f65","tid":1989420,"uid":89435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ea765c6426df761209e2c63c0c1db8282e98e50","tid":1989420,"uid":49136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3e9421e9b18f53c65e3dc0edcc9e866e9a563bcc","tid":1989420,"uid":228140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:28:47.000Z","msg":":بٍٍٍٍََُُُِّّّْرٍٍٍٍََُُِِّّّْآٍٍٍَُّ🇮🇹 بٍٍٍٍََُُُِّّّْرٍٍٍٍََُُِِّّّْآٍٍٍَُّ🇮🇹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"我試過youtube有效<br />\n大家唔好去藍youtuber試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好"},{"pid":"1cbdde9db62dc87923dcfdf984ce5a60a8690d76","tid":1989420,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"Ios 成日都有呢d 弱智野"},{"pid":"5b1310f9cd61de6ac91f114258fc13c178fbae6a","tid":1989420,"uid":241072,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72bebedff2211c9dad3ac3a8e991757857b454a3","tid":1989420,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:17:48.000